text: Baykibash () is a rural locality (a village) in Badryashevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 13 km from Badryashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Baykibash
